data.name: GetAccessories
data.value: Select AccessoriesId, AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetAccessorybyId
data.value: Select AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] where DeletedDate is null and AccessoriesId = @accessoriesId

data.name: InsertAccessory
data.value: Insert into [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] (AccessoryTypeId, Accessory, Price, CreatedDate) values (@accessoryTypeId, @accessory, @price, @createdDate)

data.name: UpdateAccessory
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Accessories] set Accessory = @accessory, Price = @price, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where AccessoriesId = @accessoriesId

data.name: GetVehicleName
data.value: Select VehicleNameId, CompanyId, VehicleName from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] where DeletedDate is null and CompanyId = @companyId

data.name: GetVehicleNamebyId
data.value: Select CompanyId, VehicleName from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] where DeletedDate is null and VehicleNameId = @vehicleNameId

data.name: UpdateVehicleName
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[VehicleName] set VehicleName = @vehicleName, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where VehicleNameId = @vehicleNameId

data.name: GetVehiclebyTransmission
data.value: Select VehicleId, VehicleNameId, VehicleVariantId, TransmissionTypeId, FuelTypeId, VehicleTypeId, CylinderArrangementId, NumberofDoors, NumberofPassenger, NumberofCylinder, EngineSize, HorsePower, Torque, Mileage, Height, Width, Length, GroundClearance, Wheelbase, FuelTankSize, KerbWeight, GrossWeight from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Vehicle] where DeletedDate is null and TransmissionTypeId = @transmissionTypeId

data.name: GetVehiclebyId
data.value: Select VehicleNameId, VehicleVariantId, TransmissionTypeId, FuelTypeId, VehicleTypeId, CylinderArrangementId, NumberofDoors, NumberofPassenger, NumberofCylinder, EngineSize, HorsePower, Torque, Mileage, Height, Width, Length, GroundClearance, Wheelbase, FuelTankSize, KerbWeight, GrossWeight from [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Vehicle] where DeletedDate is null and VehicleId = @vehicleId

data.name: InsertVehicle
UpdateVehicle
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[vehicle].[Vehicle] set VehicleNameId = @vehicleNameId, VehicleVariantId = @vehicleVariantId, TransmissionTypeId = @transmissionTypeId, FuelTypeId = @fuelTypeId, VehicleTypeId = @vehicleTYpeId, CylinderArrangementId = @cylinderArrangementId, NumberofDoors = @numberofDoors, NumberofPassenger = @numberofPassanger, NumberofCylinder = @numberofCylinder, EngineSize = @engineSize, HorsePower = @horsePower, Torque = @torque, Mileage = @mileage, Height = @height, Width = @width, Length = @length, GroundClearance = @groundClearance, Wheelbase = @wheelBase, FuelTankSize = @fuelTankSize, KerbWeight = @kerbWeight, GrossWeight = @grossWeight, ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate where VehicleId = @vehicleId
